request.description:
### Auth Login

This endpoint allows users to log in and obtain an authentication token.

#### Request Body

- `username` (string, required): The username of the user.

- `password` (string, required): The password of the user.


#### Response

The response is a JSON object with the following properties:

- `message` (string): A message related to the login process.

- `token` (string): An authentication token for the user.


#### JSON Schema

``` json
{
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
        "message": {
            "type": "string"
        },
        "token": {
            "type": "string"
        }
    }
}

 ```

The `GET` request retrieves the quiz history within a specified date range.

### Response

The response will be a JSON object with the following schema:

``` json
{
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
        "message": {
            "type": "string"
        },
        "quizHistory": {
            "type": "array",
            "items": {
                "type": "object",
                "properties": {
                    "_id": {
                        "type": "string"
                    },
                    "quizId": {
                        "type": "string"
                    },
                    "userId": {
                        "type": "string"
                    },
                    "score": {
                        "type": "number"
                    },
                    "attempt": {
                        "type": "number"
                    },
                    "completedDate": {
                        "type": "string"
                    },
                    "__v": {
                        "type": "number"
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    }
}

 ```

### API Request Description

This API endpoint allows users to retry a quiz by submitting their responses.

### API Response

The response for this request is a JSON object with the following properties:

- `message` (string): A message related to the quiz retry.

- `score` (number): The score obtained after the quiz retry.

- `all_attempts` (array): An array containing objects with the following properties:

    - `_id` (string): The unique identifier of the attempt.

    - `quizId` (string): The unique identifier of the quiz.

    - `userId` (string): The unique identifier of the user.

    - `score` (number): The score obtained in the attempt.

    - `attempt` (number): The attempt number.

    - `completedDate` (string): The date when the attempt was completed.

    - `__v` (number): Version control field.


### JSON Schema

``` json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "message": {
      "type": "string"
    },
    "score": {
      "type": "number"
    },
    "all_attempts": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "_id": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "quizId": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "userId": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "score": {
            "type": "number"
          },
          "attempt": {
            "type": "number"
          },
          "completedDate": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "__v": {
            "type": "number"
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
}

 ```
